== Linking to Anchors

You can link to anchors using HTML anchor links: `<a href="#anchor-name">Link</a>`

== Anchor Syntax

The anchor object uses the format: `{{anchor name="anchor-name"}}`

Where:
* `name` - Required anchor name attribute
